summary: I think I need to address Spider-Man for the PS4
body:
I think I need to address Spider-Man for the PS4

Today is September 28th(edit almost left 27)……Friday….. Spider-Man for the PS4 came out on the 7th in a Friday of this month.

(just had to text my mom’s sister she just told me happy Friday)

I seriously have not even played a minute of this game. Because my mindset towards story games or whatever has been fucking clouded by playing Quake Champions every single day.

Despite the fact it was a huge deal in a way my bro got pissed off that I pre ordered the game because he pre ordered the deluxe edition for me. He’s played the first mission he said it was fun.

I know of the final boss, but not the whole game, and apparently a thumbnail of a video said Harry Osborn is Venom in this universe is something.

Basically I was excited for this game but I’ve been weirdly annoyed by this positive or how game changing it is I’m like fuck it I’m gonna be playing Quake Champions, Doom games, and more first person shooters. Because I just wanna play some games…..

This is sounding ridiculous. It’s just seeing reblogs of this game from DC Vertigo Squad I can’t believe I’ve been kind of ignoring this game and being lazy.

Seriously the game sounds fucking great it’s just I’ve been lazy and weirdly turned off because my mindset has been weird.

Tags done hopefully people find this post. Seriously I need to play the game these days. Especially I’ve seen that even the official Doom Twitter weeks ago congratulated the developers behind the game with a video of the new meat hook Doomguy/Doom Slayer has. I didn’t watch the tweets video. I think u remember seeing it mentioned on some post of how this game is a super hero fantasy come true or whatever yet I’m weirdly turned off some stupid reason.

summary: It’s interesting to me that Peter exclaims “this suit is crazy intuitive” about the Iron Spider suit. It reacts almost to...
body: It’s interesting to me that Peter exclaims “this suit is crazy intuitive” about the Iron Spider suit. It reacts almost to thoughts. The waldoes pop out on their own, the mask reacts and moves on and off his face without a word. Almost like a techno symbiote. Of course it’s tech, and tony designed it. But it’s a fun thought. Like an MCU Scorn symbiote for Peter
